5.post_text:
Donnie Yen stars as a convicted former police martial arts instructor, who is released from prison to track down a vicious serial killer in KUNGFU JUNGLE 《一个人的武林》!

Want to score yourself a pair of FREE movie passes to this action-packed film? All you have to do is LIKE and SHARE this post, and answer the following question in the COMMENTS below:

"What would you say to Donnie Yen while enjoying a can of Red Bull together with him?"

Contest ends at 11:59PM on Monday, 3rd November. Red Bull Singapore will give 5 random winners a pair of FREE movie passes to catch KUNGFU JUNGLE 《一个人的武林》 in Golden Village cinemas!

The following Terms and Conditions apply.
1. Movie passes may not be sold.
2. Not valid for GV Gold Class, 3D screenings, and group bookings.
3. Not valid on Public Holidays and after 5pm on eve of Public Holidays.
4. Not valid for screenings after 5pm on Saturdays.
5. Subject to seat availability.
6. Valid until film run ends.
